OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine day for many with plenty
OL,6,Fof sunshine, although low cloud may
OL,7,Faffect Cumbria and areas near to the
OL,8,Fcoast at times. Sunshine may turn a
OL,9,Flittle hazy elsewhere throughout the
OL,10,Fafternoon, but feeling very warm for
OL,11,Fmost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning rather cloudy this
OL,14,Fevening with some outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fmoving across the region overnight.
OL,16,FDrier again by dawn but skies
OL,17,Fremaining rather cloudy for many. A
OL,18,Fmild night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
