OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA grey start in places, but
OL,6,Fthe cloud will increasingly break up
OL,7,Fallowing plenty of sunshine to develop
OL,8,Facross the region come of the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Feeling a little fresher.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,12,FRemaining dry and settled throughout
OL,13,FSunday and early next week with plenty
OL,14,Fof sunshine. Feeling very warm by day
OL,15,Fwith potentially some warm nights too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
